	<a class="event" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/International-Conference-Innovations-in-Extension-and-Advisory-Services-Linking-Knowledge-to-Policy-and-Action-for-Food-and-Livelihoods">Read more...</a>
