						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/K4D-Marketing-Communication-Outreach-Survey" title="K4D Marketing Communication Outreach Survey" alt="link">K4D Marketing Communication Outreach Survey</a></h2>

	
					<p>The Science, Technology and Innovation Strategies Programme at CTA is conducting a <b>short survey</b> to assist with developing a marketing, communication and outreach strategy for the Knowledge for Development (K4D) portal <a href="http://knowledge.cta.int" target="_blank">http://knowledge.cta.int</a> .The main idea is to produce a strategy to promote discussion and engage more scientists including young professionals and other stakeholders in the ST&amp;I dialogue on the K4D website in support of ACP agricultural and rural development. The survey will not take more than ten (10) minutes.Please follow the link below to start the survey:<a href="http://www.surveymonkey.com/s/Q3MGSNY" target="_blank">http://www.surveymonkey.com/s/Q3MGSNY</a>Thank you for your cooperation.Miriam Sengi (Intern)<b>CTA will very much appreciate your views and suggestions to help improve this service</b>
On behalf of








 




  
  

	
	<a href="/var/knowledge/storage/images/media/images/logos/cta-logo-single/219178-2-eng-GB/CTA-logo-single.png" rel="lightbox[]" >	
	  </a>
	
	
	
	
  	






	 
  





	Judith Ann FrancisSenior Programme CoordinatorScience &amp; Technology StrategiesCTA</p>
							<p><span class="date">21/04/2011</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
